Name: Tracadie Bird Shit
About the game: Play as a bird in a small city called Tracadie and make the right choices to be able to complete the story. There will be a lot of yelling and weird situations so if you're into that 'absurd humor' this game might interest you. This game is a simple visual novel where clicking is the only thing you will need to do to progress in the story. Key Features -Funny Story -French Voice Acting -Choices Matter
